Comment: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I am Isabella York.
Comment: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This is my prison.
Comment: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:52.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,, A women's garden, guarded from the outside by tall walls.
Comment: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:56.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where only royal ladies and their handmaidsare ever allowed.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The only students in this school...
Comment: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are those who either aspire to attain high status or those who want to be brides.
Comment: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I fear that I might belong to the latter.
Comment: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:12.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, she can go anywhere.
Comment: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you.
Comment: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We shall hasten anywhere a customer requests us.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Dolls at your service.
Comment: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm Violet Evergarden.
Comment: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why would a Doll come here?
Comment: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We were requested by...
Comment: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The York family to help Lady Isabella's debut.
Comment: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Turn into a success.
Comment: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My debut?
Comment: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's in three months.
Comment: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.78,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Until then you shall be taught proper manners, conversation topics, etiquette...
Comment: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,and dancing.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's the job we've been commended.
Comment: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,From today onward, I shall be your personal tutor.
Comment: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So Dolls can be hired for that kind of  work too.
Comment: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. Originally our job is only to write letters.
Comment: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Without the Drossel family's referral
Comment: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,we would have declined.
Comment: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So you think you're too important.
Comment: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I really hate that kind of people.
Comment: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We were told about your breathing issues.
Comment: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Comment: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Your hand...
Comment: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,They're prosthetic.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I lost them in the war.
Comment: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you a kingdom servant Doll?
Comment: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. I'm only a civilian Doll.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Our firm is located at Leidenschaflic.
Comment: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Leiden?
Comment: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,A country south of the continent.
Comment: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:17.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,With the transcontinental railroad,  we have regular trains connecting us.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It takes 4 days of travel.
Comment: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You can go anywhere you please in the whole world.
Comment: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm requested to.
Comment: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter.
Comment: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I shall accompany you until my job is done.
Comment: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on humoring you.
Comment: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Only talk to me when it's necessary.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,For my lessons.
Comment: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Again with your troubled look.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it really something so important?
Comment: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:58.30,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah...It's about that request for Violet-chan.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The one about being a tutor for the royal lady.
Comment: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Tutor?
Comment: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And for three months too.
Comment: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You'd have refused.Wasn't it for the king. Huh?
Comment: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And for three months!
Comment: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:15.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How about I go check on her from time to time?
Comment: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:19.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's in a school that doesn't allow boys, you know?
Comment: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,An all female school...
Comment: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This public love letter,sure is wonderful.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I made it the other day.
Comment: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Marvelous!
Comment: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.46,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You can have it if you wish.
Comment: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Comment: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My... Who could she be?
Comment: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her before.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.22,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Comment: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. I've never seen her either.
Comment: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.46,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miss York.
Comment: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Miss York.
Comment: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And who is with you?
Comment: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,From today on,I'll be Isabella's handmaiden.
Comment: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My name is Violet.
Comment: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I see... I am...
Comment: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Miss Lancaster, correct?
Comment: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I was informed of your name.
Comment: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What a refined greeting.
Comment: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She looks more like a princess than a maid.
Comment: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Please use the outermost knife.
Comment: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,MiladyYou've stopped writing.
Comment: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You need to keep practicing.This is a fundamental subject.
Comment: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I(boku)...
Comment: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No more "boku"Please use "watakushi" instead.
Comment: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor!
Comment: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor!
Comment: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:31.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne loves you, Taylor. I love you.
Comment: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Which salon will you be joiningMiss York?
Comment: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She will joinMiss Lancaster's Salon, of course, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Lancaster, the prime minister familyAnd York, the renowned merchants.
Comment: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Along with the Drossels The families...
Comment: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We cannot apologize enough.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Milady Isabella is in a delicate state.
Comment: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She has spent many days in confinement. And now she has to adjust...
Comment: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,To a more social lifestyle.However she requires some time.
Comment: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,May we excuse her for her behavior meanwhile?
Comment: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:42.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!She speaks like a knight!
Comment: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Milady Isabella!
Comment: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I am very sorryfor leaving your side.
Comment: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,When I look at you...
Comment: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I feel really pathetic.
Comment: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor...
Comment: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How have you been, Miss York?
Comment: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:35.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We will go back to the dormitory soon.And we will have tea.
Comment: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:36.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,If you wish to...
Comment: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.90,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How annoying!
Comment: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, did you say something?
Comment: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I must apologize.
Comment: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:48.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The master has asked us to refrain from any extra curricular activities...
Comment: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Until the time of Milady's debut.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You truly are a "knight-princess," I see.
Comment: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:58.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It is fine.I will leave it at that for now.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.58,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Stay well.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:08.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Those girls don't care aboutanything but families' names.
Comment: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,They only seek the honors bestowed by it.
Comment: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And you're same, aren't you?
Comment: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I only seek to carry out my duties.
Comment: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You truly are the image of "perfection," huh?
Comment: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,As long as some authority tells you something, you don't even doubt.
Comment: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm an orphan.
Comment: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay? You being here 3 months.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ignoring me?
Comment: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You told me notto talk to you...
Comment: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Unless it was necessary for your lessons.
Comment: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then, just for today.
Comment: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The company has other dolls as well. So if you're dissatisfied with...
Comment: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Comment: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Don't you have, like,  anyone you miss, or something?
Comment: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So there is one.
Comment: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,There is someone I miss.
Comment: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yet I can never see him again.
Comment: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.66,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Will she be alright?Violet-chan...
Comment: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor...
Comment: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. This is Violet.
Comment: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Comment: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Were you awake all this time?
Comment: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm used to long drills.
Comment: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I only need little slee-
Comment: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Comment: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So...
Comment: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,As girls of around the same age...
Comment: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I want to talk normally, you know.
Comment: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Comment: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But talking normally...What kind of talk would that be?
Comment: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Let's see, for example.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:31.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We must get ready.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Or we will be late for school.
Comment: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Basicallythe students in this school
Comment: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,learn dance movesfor both men and women.
Comment: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama, you first get the women's role.
Comment: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I will perform the men's.
Comment: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But... I will definitely end upstepping on you.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The trick to improve...
Comment: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:10.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is to relax all your unnecessary tension and follow your partner.
Comment: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Milady Isabella.
Comment: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why don't you get in?
Comment: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Comment: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Friends can go into the bath together.
Comment: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Comment: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's totally true, you know?
Comment: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So...
Comment: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.90,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is a first.
Comment: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Getting in a bath with someone else.
Comment: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Comment: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Another activity for friends?
Comment: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.82,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Comment: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:51.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I used to sleep like this with my little sister.
Comment: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You did?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.90,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Open wide, Taylor.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Tastes good?
Comment: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You already got the basics almost perfectly.
Comment: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Today we will startadding variations.
Comment: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.70,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Comment: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It is done.
Comment: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You always use the same hairstyle, right?
Comment: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I do.
Comment: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama?
Comment: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:49.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Stay still now.
Comment: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:56.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This concerns me.We will be late for the morning lessons.
Comment: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Comment: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:03.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I used to do my sisters hair up all the time.
Comment: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Your hair...It feels like velvet.
Comment: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It would sell very well.
Comment: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Will you sell it?
Comment: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nah... I'm not gonna sell it.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.34,Engsub,,0,0,0,,There! All done!
Comment: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.30,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How you like it?
Comment: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:24.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Seems like it could obstruct my viewin the case of an emergency.
Comment: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And? It looks cute...
Comment: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Comment: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Sheep horns!
Comment: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama,are you messing around?
Comment: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.54,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You noticed?
Comment: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:47.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:51.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Let's ditch class!We could go somewhere else instead.
Comment: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where?
Comment: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:00.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Being together...
Comment: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We can't just go anywhere,
Comment: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama.
Comment: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Alright, now again from that point.
Comment: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama?
Comment: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Comment: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:54.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me.To be a lady.
Comment: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You've learned the danceand etiquette pretty well.
Comment: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't need your compliments!
Comment: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,There is not a single thing I can do as well as you.
Comment: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:08.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We are different.
Comment: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:10.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Different?
Comment: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:13.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's right! We're polar opposites!
Comment: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You're so unfair!
Comment: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:19.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You have been blessed so much.
Comment: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:25.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You must be a little tired.
Comment: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:48.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What kind of lettershave you written so far?
Comment: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:53.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wrote a lot of letters.
Comment: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:58.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,From parents to children and back.From little sisters to big brothers.
Comment: 0,0:23:58.64,0:24:00.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And love letters too.
Comment: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:03.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Love letters?Even when you're so formal.
Comment: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm actually popular for that.
Comment: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:13.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Every letter has had one or otherway of saying "I love you."
Comment: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:17.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Letters can communicate...
Comment: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.90,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What is in the heart and can't normally be said.
Comment: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:28.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So... Why?
Comment: 0,0:24:30.52,0:24:33.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I am... Awful...
Comment: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:37.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But you have been so kind to me?
Comment: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:38.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've been kind?
Comment: 0,0:24:39.48,0:24:41.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You have.
Comment: 0,0:24:41.84,0:24:45.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm just acting my part.
Comment: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:53.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama,if you aren't sleepy...
Comment: 0,0:24:53.16,0:24:55.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I can tell you a story about the stars.
Comment: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:59.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I learned it back when I worked in an observatory.
Comment: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:00.78,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:25:01.44,0:25:04.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then... I'll tell you a story about the stars
Comment: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:07.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,that can be seen shinning over here.
Comment: 0,0:25:14.56,0:25:15.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Comment: 0,0:25:16.28,0:25:17.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's from your father.
Comment: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:21.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So you can wear them on your debut.
Comment: 0,0:25:39.32,0:25:40.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Comment: 0,0:25:46.52,0:25:47.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Comment: 0,0:25:48.72,0:25:52.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Are you having fun?"What is this?
Comment: 0,0:25:52.88,0:25:55.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My dress is provided by the company.
Comment: 0,0:25:56.00,0:26:00.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I imagine this was sent by one of my coworkers.
Comment: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:05.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Don't they mean something like "We want you to come back soon?"
Comment: 0,0:26:10.04,0:26:12.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You go back home today?
Comment: 0,0:26:12.48,0:26:15.04,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will leave tonight.
Comment: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:16.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then...
Comment: 0,0:26:18.00,0:26:21.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy the ball a whole lot, okay?
Comment: 0,0:26:23.80,0:26:26.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,May you allow me to lead?
Comment: 0,0:26:34.84,0:26:36.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Gladly.
Comment: 0,0:27:04.52,0:27:06.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Everyone is looking at you.
Comment: 0,0:27:07.12,0:27:09.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Do I look weird?
Comment: 0,0:27:09.24,0:27:11.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Comment: 0,0:27:11.92,0:27:13.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's because you're so pretty.
Comment: 0,0:27:13.68,0:27:16.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yet everyone is so well dressed.
Comment: 0,0:27:16.52,0:27:19.08,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You're the prettiest in the room.
Comment: 0,0:27:20.88,0:27:23.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey... Please don't leave my side.
Comment: 0,0:27:25.92,0:27:28.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I will not. I promise.
Comment: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:44.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Isabella-sama.
Comment: 0,0:28:08.00,0:28:10.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Violet.
Comment: 0,0:28:15.24,0:28:16.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Always.
Comment: 0,0:29:57.36,0:29:58.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Comment: 0,0:29:59.20,0:30:00.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:30:01.16,0:30:02.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:30:03.48,0:30:04.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It was fun!
Comment: 0,0:30:06.16,0:30:08.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And I didn't step on you at all!
Comment: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:10.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You did not.
Comment: 0,0:30:13.44,0:30:15.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What will you do after this?
Comment: 0,0:30:15.27,0:30:18.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Write letters.As I've been doing.
Comment: 0,0:30:22.36,0:30:23.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Say...
Comment: 0,0:30:25.64,0:30:26.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Could you...
Comment: 0,0:30:27.72,0:30:29.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Write a letter for me.
Comment: 0,0:30:30.28,0:30:31.42,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Whom to?
Comment: 0,0:30:34.00,0:30:36.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My little sister.
Comment: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:41.70,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wasn't born a heir to the York family.
Comment: 0,0:30:51.52,0:30:52.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy!
Comment: 0,0:30:54.60,0:30:57.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This time go get me something better.
Comment: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:06.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,They're not easy to findthanks to the war.
Comment: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:23.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where is your mom?
Comment: 0,0:31:34.40,0:31:36.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Another abandoned kid?
Comment: 0,0:31:36.84,0:31:40.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,God! They might not turn good moneyif you sell them but at least...
Comment: 0,0:32:12.00,0:32:12.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Comment: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:16.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'll make her my sister.
Comment: 0,0:32:16.96,0:32:20.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Cut the crap.
Comment: 0,0:32:20.36,0:32:23.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's not like you have an easy life.Do you think you can handle it?
Comment: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:27.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,On top of thatyou're still a kid yourself.
Comment: 0,0:32:28.24,0:32:29.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's my revenge.
Comment: 0,0:32:29.35,0:32:32.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I won't let her live such kind of life.
Comment: 0,0:32:34.08,0:32:36.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This child is supposedto be miserable.
Comment: 0,0:32:37.20,0:32:39.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But I'll make her happy instead.
Comment: 0,0:32:40.20,0:32:43.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give her the choices I never had.
Comment: 0,0:32:45.64,0:32:48.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that revenge?
Comment: 0,0:32:49.36,0:32:51.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't care, you both can go die out there.
Comment: 0,0:32:55.48,0:32:57.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You will be my little sister now.
Comment: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Comment: 0,0:33:03.04,0:33:06.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then... Onee-chan?
Comment: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:12.78,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ne... Ne... Ne...
Comment: 0,0:33:14.84,0:33:16.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:34:08.96,0:34:09.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Comment: 0,0:34:10.08,0:34:12.64,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:34:22.32,0:34:23.54,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Here, Taylor.
Comment: 0,0:34:28.08,0:34:29.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it tasty?
Comment: 0,0:34:32.04,0:34:33.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:34:37.64,0:34:39.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,In a dirty room.
Comment: 0,0:34:40.80,0:34:43.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,With not a single pretty thing to see.
Comment: 0,0:34:45.20,0:34:47.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But back then...
Comment: 0,0:34:47.92,0:34:50.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I didn't need anything else.
Comment: 0,0:35:01.88,0:35:03.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:35:10.16,0:35:12.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You're Amy Bartlett, correct?
Comment: 0,0:35:12.64,0:35:14.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How dare you barge in like that!!
Comment: 0,0:35:14.96,0:35:17.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So these are the girls from that incident.
Comment: 0,0:35:18.08,0:35:21.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Blood of my blood.The York family.
Comment: 0,0:35:22.76,0:35:24.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My daughter.
Comment: 0,0:35:29.76,0:35:32.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Drop your name, your past and come with us.
Comment: 0,0:35:32.72,0:35:33.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,If you do...
Comment: 0,0:35:35.04,0:35:38.82,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We will be taking care of that girl too.
Comment: 0,0:35:42.52,0:35:44.82,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's better for her too.
Comment: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:49.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can keep living like this?
Comment: 0,0:35:55.20,0:35:56.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:03.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My life has no meaning.
Comment: 0,0:36:03.40,0:36:05.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Neither has passion, nor hope.
Comment: 0,0:36:06.80,0:36:11.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,If only there was a single thing I couldcall wonderful...
Comment: 0,0:36:13.60,0:36:14.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,0:36:15.88,0:36:17.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!!
Comment: 0,0:36:18.96,0:36:21.34,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!!
Comment: 0,0:36:21.72,0:36:24.52,Engsub,,0,0,0,,To think there would be somethingI wanted to protect so much.
Comment: 0,0:36:24.64,0:36:26.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Something I wanted to save so much....
Comment: 0,0:36:27.20,0:36:29.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That should become my reason to live.
Comment: 0,0:36:29.40,0:36:31.70,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:36:32.80,0:36:34.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Comment: 0,0:36:34.24,0:36:37.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I sold my life to a man who calledhimself my father.
Comment: 0,0:36:40.76,0:36:43.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This is my, or rather Amy's past.
Comment: 0,0:36:44.40,0:36:48.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,From that moment I've been apart from Taylor.
Comment: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:51.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm not allowed to see her.
Comment: 0,0:36:52.96,0:36:56.66,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We are a bit... alike.
Comment: 0,0:36:58.72,0:37:03.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've never seen my parents. I was abandoned.Then raised as a weapon.
Comment: 0,0:37:04.12,0:37:06.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And then I met that man.
Comment: 0,0:37:07.52,0:37:11.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,He taught me how to read,and he raised me.
Comment: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:13.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,With kindness.
Comment: 0,0:37:15.52,0:37:19.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,He has also given me a reason to live.
Comment: 0,0:37:22.16,0:37:25.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I couldn't give you anything in the end.
Comment: 0,0:37:26.44,0:37:30.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No, Isabella-sama.
Comment: 0,0:37:30.64,0:37:33.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You have given me my first "friend."
Comment: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:35.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And...
Comment: 0,0:37:36.44,0:37:37.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You have taught me...
Comment: 0,0:37:38.56,0:37:43.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That holding hands can makemy heart get warmer.
Comment: 0,0:37:44.36,0:37:47.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I believe that you were able to grant Taylor-sama
Comment: 0,0:37:48.08,0:37:50.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,a lot of things too.
Comment: 0,0:37:55.16,0:37:58.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,With a letter, your feelings, Isabella-sama.
Comment: 0,0:37:58.24,0:38:00.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No matter how far,will for sure reach her.
Comment: 0,0:38:02.08,0:38:03.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:38:15.20,0:38:16.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor...
Comment: 0,0:38:40.64,0:38:42.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Someday I will pay you.
Comment: 0,0:38:43.36,0:38:47.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Right now I have nothing to give you.
Comment: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:49.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But I will surely repay you.
Comment: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:51.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that.
Comment: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:55.38,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why? I will pay you!
Comment: 0,0:38:56.44,0:38:59.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand it myself, but...
Comment: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:04.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I simply don't want to take it.
Comment: 0,0:39:10.32,0:39:11.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Say...
Comment: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:14.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Will we meet again?
Comment: 0,0:39:14.96,0:39:16.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:39:19.16,0:39:21.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But... Amy-sama.
Comment: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:25.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm an Auto Memory Doll.
Comment: 0,0:39:26.08,0:39:29.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We shall hasten anywhere a customer requests us.
Comment: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:07.78,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Your knight-princess is gone I see...
Comment: 0,0:40:12.44,0:40:15.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We can finally have a chat alone.
Comment: 0,0:40:17.72,0:40:20.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Your debut's waltz really is marvelous.
Comment: 0,0:40:21.96,0:40:25.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Violet.
Comment: 0,0:40:25.76,0:40:27.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Miss Lancaster.
Comment: 0,0:40:27.92,0:40:29.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You can call me Ashley.
Comment: 0,0:40:31.96,0:40:34.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I don't care about family names.
Comment: 0,0:40:35.92,0:40:39.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to have a chatwith your real self.
Comment: 0,0:41:04.92,0:41:06.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Comment: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:10.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I have two letters for you.
Comment: 0,0:41:11.08,0:41:13.64,Engsub,,0,0,0,, For me? For Taylor?
Comment: 0,0:41:13.76,0:41:15.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're for you.
Comment: 0,0:41:19.44,0:41:22.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Lady!You know if this kid can read?
Comment: 0,0:41:23.24,0:41:24.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She can't.
Comment: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:30.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I guess we will have to...
Comment: 0,0:41:31.52,0:41:34.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I will read it for you.Okay?
Comment: 0,0:41:34.88,0:41:37.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Tylar!  Here we go...
Comment: 0,0:41:38.08,0:41:39.22,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Niini!
Comment: 0,0:41:39.36,0:41:41.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a Niini?
Comment: 0,0:41:41.56,0:41:43.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Alright, listen well.
Comment: 0,0:41:44.20,0:41:47.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,First: From Violet Evergarden.
Comment: 0,0:41:47.28,0:41:49.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's my coworker.
Comment: 0,0:41:49.28,0:41:51.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It says that if you have any worries or
Comment: 0,0:41:52.52,0:41:54.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,need anything you should ask her.
Comment: 0,0:41:54.24,0:41:57.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This doesn't have a sender.
Comment: 0,0:41:58.08,0:41:59.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's so short!
Comment: 0,0:42:00.56,0:42:04.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"This is a magic spellto keep you safe."
Comment: 0,0:42:05.44,0:42:09.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Amy." Just recite that...
Comment: 0,0:42:09.52,0:42:10.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,End.
Comment: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:19.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey Taylor.
Comment: 0,0:42:20.08,0:42:24.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy... is no longer a name you can call...
Comment: 0,0:42:25.40,0:42:27.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's a name I've thrown away out of love for you.
Comment: 0,0:42:35.76,0:42:37.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:42:37.52,0:42:40.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,As long as you recite itlike a magic spell.
Comment: 0,0:42:41.24,0:42:42.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,0:42:44.84,0:42:48.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It will forever remain as...
Comment: 0,0:42:49.76,0:42:53.30,Engsub,,0,0,0,,As my wish that you may be happy.
Comment: 0,0:42:56.08,0:42:58.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,0:43:05.20,0:43:06.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So Taylor...
Comment: 0,0:43:17.92,0:43:19.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Comment: 0,0:43:19.27,0:43:28.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Call that name if you ever feel lonely.
Comment: 0,0:43:55.56,0:43:57.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery.
Comment: 0,0:44:03.16,0:44:04.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery!
Comment: 0,0:44:10.36,0:44:11.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:44:13.32,0:44:16.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Fields-san isn't home again...
Comment: 0,0:44:16.36,0:44:20.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Even thoughthey were so lively last night.
Comment: 0,0:44:20.92,0:44:22.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Should I keep the package for him?
Comment: 0,0:44:23.44,0:44:27.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nah.This has to be paid on delivery, so I'll be back tonight.
Comment: 0,0:44:30.24,0:44:32.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey!Don't go around touching my stuff!
Comment: 0,0:44:34.00,0:44:36.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Run! That bike is scrap!
Comment: 0,0:44:45.52,0:44:46.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery!
Comment: 0,0:44:47.32,0:44:48.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery?
Comment: 0,0:44:49.76,0:44:51.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks as always.
Comment: 0,0:44:52.40,0:44:54.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We will be waiting for your next request
Comment: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:17.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where did that deliveryman go!?
Comment: 0,0:45:25.56,0:45:26.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Delivery.
Comment: 0,0:45:31.24,0:45:32.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir...
Comment: 0,0:45:34.48,0:45:39.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What was that tall buildingagain?
Comment: 0,0:45:41.04,0:45:43.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I told you! It's a radio tower!
Comment: 0,0:45:44.00,0:45:45.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Radio? What's that?
Comment: 0,0:45:45.84,0:45:49.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That thing better not give any headaches!
Comment: 0,0:45:49.28,0:45:52.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It won't.
Comment: 0,0:45:52.64,0:45:53.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's been there for 4 years!
Comment: 0,0:45:54.16,0:45:55.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,After the war ended!
Comment: 0,0:45:59.00,0:46:01.30,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The world has kept progressing in many ways.
Comment: 0,0:46:06.44,0:46:09.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No matter how much the worldkeeps spinning and progressing.
Comment: 0,0:46:09.68,0:46:13.30,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The job of deliverymenhasn't changed at all.
Comment: 0,0:46:15.88,0:46:17.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Everyday, we just keep doing the same.
Comment: 0,0:46:20.40,0:46:22.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's a boring job.
Comment: 0,0:46:31.08,0:46:32.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's the same sign.
Comment: 0,0:46:43.52,0:46:44.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nii-...
Comment: 0,0:46:45.60,0:46:47.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Niini!
Comment: 0,0:46:52.04,0:46:53.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Niini!
Comment: 0,0:46:56.60,0:47:00.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,A lost child?
Comment: 0,0:47:00.60,0:47:03.16,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Benedict's younger brother?
Comment: 0,0:47:04.56,0:47:06.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps an bastard son?
Comment: 0,0:47:07.32,0:47:10.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No way! It's a customer!
Comment: 0,0:47:13.52,0:47:15.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm...
Comment: 0,0:47:18.92,0:47:22.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor. Taylor Bartlett.
Comment: 0,0:47:22.68,0:47:25.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She was a girl!?
Comment: 0,0:47:31.48,0:47:33.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you Taylor-sama?
Comment: 0,0:47:34.16,0:47:35.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:47:35.48,0:47:37.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you, Bialet Evergatten?
Comment: 0,0:47:38.12,0:47:39.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of mistakes.
Comment: 0,0:47:42.88,0:47:45.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This!A letter you wrote me 3 years ago.
Comment: 0,0:47:46.24,0:47:49.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You said:"If you need something come ask me!"
Comment: 0,0:47:49.56,0:47:51.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So I came here!
Comment: 0,0:47:54.12,0:47:55.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She's that one...
Comment: 0,0:47:57.04,0:47:59.60,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So is there anything troubling you?
Comment: 0,0:48:01.32,0:48:02.46,Engsub,,0,0,0,, I have a request.
Comment: 0,0:48:03.84,0:48:05.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:48:06.16,0:48:07.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Wanna work here!
Comment: 0,0:48:11.00,0:48:12.22,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Here...
Comment: 0,0:48:13.60,0:48:16.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"If you ever leave the the orphanage..."
Comment: 0,0:48:16.84,0:48:21.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"And you have any trouble please come see me."
Comment: 0,0:48:21.52,0:48:24.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Signed: “Violet Evergarden“
Comment: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:29.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:48:33.40,0:48:35.70,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor-chan I hate to ask but...
Comment: 0,0:48:36.44,0:48:38.74,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Did you run away fromthe orphanage?
Comment: 0,0:48:39.08,0:48:42.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a single orphanagein the kingdom of Drossel
Comment: 0,0:48:43.36,0:48:47.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,that would allow a kid your age to leave.
Comment: 0,0:48:48.52,0:48:49.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,0:48:54.56,0:48:55.54,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Comment: 0,0:48:58.32,0:49:01.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Also, to work here...
Comment: 0,0:49:01.24,0:49:04.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wish you could wait until you're a bitmore grown-up, you see?
Comment: 0,0:49:04.36,0:49:08.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No way... I beg you!I don't have any money left!
Comment: 0,0:49:09.24,0:49:10.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,All the more reason...
Comment: 0,0:49:10.56,0:49:12.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I beg of you too.
Comment: 0,0:49:13.48,0:49:15.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Violet...chan?
Comment: 0,0:49:16.48,0:49:18.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She's my friend's...
Comment: 0,0:49:18.72,0:49:22.34,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Beloved little sister.
Comment: 0,0:49:28.16,0:49:30.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,, I want to know! The meaning of "I love you."
Comment: 0,0:49:32.04,0:49:33.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Comment: 0,0:49:40.28,0:49:44.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Well... Even if we send her home,it's gonna take some time.
Comment: 0,0:49:44.44,0:49:46.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We would need to gather information...
Comment: 0,0:49:47.16,0:49:47.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then...
Comment: 0,0:49:48.48,0:49:50.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yup. Meanwhile...
Comment: 0,0:49:50.72,0:49:53.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan will be taking care of her.
Comment: 0,0:49:53.44,0:49:54.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Comment: 0,0:49:56.44,0:49:58.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Comment: 0,0:49:58.56,0:50:01.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then she'll be a writing assistant?
Comment: 0,0:50:01.64,0:50:03.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,, No! That's not right!
Comment: 0,0:50:04.72,0:50:08.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I want to be a deliveryman!
Comment: 0,0:50:08.48,0:50:09.46,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery?
Comment: 0,0:50:09.92,0:50:12.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,...Deliveryman?
Comment: 0,0:50:15.76,0:50:19.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be a writing assistant,Taylor-chan?
Comment: 0,0:50:19.52,0:50:21.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Before I came here
Comment: 0,0:50:21.56,0:50:24.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I decided that I wanted to bea deliveryman!
Comment: 0,0:50:24.32,0:50:27.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,, There is no way.This isn't a job for brats!
Comment: 0,0:50:27.80,0:50:29.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,, No way! I asked you please!
Comment: 0,0:50:29.96,0:50:37.00,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Niini! Hey! Please Niini!
Comment: 0,0:50:32.10,0:50:33.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Who are you calling Niini!
Comment: 0,0:50:33.70,0:50:35.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I beg of you too.
Comment: 0,0:50:35.59,0:50:37.40,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You too...
Comment: 0,0:50:37.40,0:50:39.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,, That's good,Benedict.
Comment: 0,0:50:40.44,0:50:43.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's a good chance.At least you could make her your apprentice.
Comment: 0,0:50:43.92,0:50:46.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,See... the boss spoke.
Comment: 0,0:50:56.28,0:50:57.42,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Comment: 0,0:50:57.56,0:51:00.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The work of a deliverymanmight seem easy
Comment: 0,0:51:00.76,0:51:02.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,but it's a great effort!
Comment: 0,0:51:02.56,0:51:05.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,First you take a quota of mails.
Comment: 0,0:51:06.48,0:51:07.70,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And deliver them.
Comment: 0,0:51:08.76,0:51:10.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Comment: 0,0:51:11.12,0:51:13.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,To the addresses written on the envelopes, of course.
Comment: 0,0:51:13.88,0:51:15.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Here, try one.
Comment: 0,0:51:20.32,0:51:23.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,2... 1...
Comment: 0,0:51:23.36,0:51:24.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Leiden City, Mill district.
Comment: 0,0:51:25.20,0:51:28.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Alexandre Road 2125.
Comment: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:31.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Comment: 0,0:51:31.88,0:51:33.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah! The Mill district.
Comment: 0,0:51:33.64,0:51:34.86,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Mill district.
Comment: 0,0:51:38.12,0:51:39.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it here?
Comment: 0,0:51:40.00,0:51:40.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:51:51.24,0:51:52.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Comment: 0,0:51:55.96,0:51:57.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Huh? There is no mailbox.
Comment: 0,0:51:58.00,0:52:00.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then you have to deliver to their room.
Comment: 0,0:52:02.52,0:52:04.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Fourth floor!
Comment: 0,0:52:04.36,0:52:05.58,Engsub,,0,0,0,, To the next.
Comment: 0,0:52:27.52,0:52:29.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Comment: 0,0:52:29.80,0:52:30.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We're going back.
Comment: 0,0:52:32.32,0:52:33.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Comment: 0,0:52:35.68,0:52:38.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You deliver so many every day.
Comment: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:43.26,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And you haven't even lookedat the map the whole day.
Comment: 0,0:52:43.72,0:52:44.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Comment: 0,0:52:46.72,0:52:48.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Deliverymen...
Comment: 0,0:52:48.32,0:52:51.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Keep all the directionsin their heads. It's normal.
Comment: 0,0:52:53.52,0:52:54.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Niini...
Comment: 0,0:52:55.32,0:52:56.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:52:58.44,0:53:00.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Say! Can I call you master?
Comment: 0,0:53:01.00,0:53:03.56,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't do that.
Comment: 0,0:53:09.60,0:53:12.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The lamps turn on because of me!
Comment: 0,0:53:12.68,0:53:16.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,, A decree of city planning made them replace the lanterns.
Comment: 0,0:53:21.44,0:53:24.00,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to becomea deliveryman or whatever?
Comment: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:28.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No "whatever!"
Comment: 0,0:53:32.76,0:53:36.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It was because deliverymen  bring happiness.
Comment: 0,0:53:41.76,0:53:43.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is this room for me?
Comment: 0,0:53:43.96,0:53:44.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:53:46.28,0:53:47.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And Bialet's room?
Comment: 0,0:53:48.44,0:53:51.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's downstairs, at the other side.
Comment: 0,0:53:51.92,0:53:55.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So this my own room!
Comment: 0,0:53:59.44,0:54:02.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Master! See you tomorrow!
Comment: 0,0:54:05.32,0:54:09.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey... You still don't know how to read, do you?
Comment: 0,0:54:10.72,0:54:13.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Today you weren't able to read a single address.
Comment: 0,0:54:14.52,0:54:15.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You only read the numbers.
Comment: 0,0:54:21.12,0:54:24.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's true. I can't read.
Comment: 0,0:54:24.40,0:54:28.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I have trouble memorizing the characters.
Comment: 0,0:54:28.96,0:54:32.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I had a nun read the letters for me all the time.
Comment: 0,0:54:32.92,0:54:36.54,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"This is...  A magic word to keep you safe."
Comment: 0,0:54:37.32,0:54:40.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,“Amy.You only need to recite that. “
Comment: 0,0:54:42.44,0:54:44.90,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Sister...Yes?
Comment: 0,0:54:47.80,0:54:50.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Read it again.
Comment: 0,0:54:55.12,0:54:58.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for keeping...
Comment: 0,0:54:59.24,0:55:00.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So many secrets.
Comment: 0,0:55:06.96,0:55:08.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor-sama.
Comment: 0,0:55:10.72,0:55:13.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I will teach you how to read.
Comment: 0,0:55:13.28,0:55:15.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:55:16.20,0:55:19.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.Tomorrow we will have a drill together.
Comment: 0,0:55:20.60,0:55:22.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Drill?
Comment: 0,0:55:22.96,0:55:26.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No... I mean that we will study together.
Comment: 0,0:55:27.80,0:55:33.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Study and aim to becomea deliveryman when you grow up.
Comment: 0,0:55:36.00,0:55:38.38,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Bialet...
Comment: 0,0:55:41.68,0:55:43.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's... Violet.
Comment: 0,0:56:16.36,0:56:21.38,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it lame to not want to sleep alonedespite not being a baby anymore?
Comment: 0,0:56:21.96,0:56:23.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Comment: 0,0:56:25.76,0:56:28.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Looking outside?
Comment: 0,0:56:29.20,0:56:30.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Mine is a bear!
Comment: 0,0:56:31.84,0:56:35.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I have slept on the same bed as your sister, Taylor-sama.
Comment: 0,0:56:36.96,0:56:39.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,For real? Did you sleep together?
Comment: 0,0:56:40.08,0:56:41.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:56:41.52,0:56:44.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:56:46.60,0:56:50.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Nenne used to sleep with me.
Comment: 0,0:57:01.00,0:57:04.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear about Nenne!
Comment: 0,0:57:15.84,0:57:18.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor-sama, it's morning.
Comment: 0,0:57:30.04,0:57:31.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:58:15.44,0:58:19.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Only two locks end up coming apart, Taylor-sama.
Comment: 0,0:58:39.08,0:58:42.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,, You need to take three of them.Then they won't get undone.
Comment: 0,0:58:47.08,0:58:49.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning!Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:58:51.48,0:58:52.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:59:01.00,0:59:04.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My, good morning.Our cute new employee.
Comment: 0,0:59:04.92,0:59:08.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Rolland-san? I thought you had retired already?
Comment: 0,0:59:10.40,0:59:14.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I just have so much time now.I wanted to pay a visit.
Comment: 0,0:59:14.52,0:59:15.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,By the way, Violet.
Comment: 0,0:59:16.72,0:59:20.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you here to givethe deliverymen a hand?
Comment: 0,0:59:25.52,0:59:28.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,, "A" is for Atashi (me).
Comment: 0,0:59:28.52,0:59:31.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"I" Is for "itsumo" (Always).
Comment: 0,0:59:31.56,0:59:34.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"U" is for "ureshii" (happiness)
Comment: 0,0:59:34.52,0:59:37.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So much fun every day!
Comment: 0,0:59:37.84,0:59:40.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"E" is for "egao" (smile).
Comment: 0,0:59:39.44,0:59:40.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Violet!?
Comment: 0,0:59:41.56,0:59:42.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Luculia...
Comment: 0,0:59:46.00,0:59:47.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Comment: 0,0:59:47.84,0:59:50.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed like that?
Comment: 0,0:59:51.08,0:59:52.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We're deliverymen!
Comment: 0,0:59:52.84,0:59:55.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Deliverymen? This girl too?
Comment: 0,0:59:57.72,0:59:59.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She's an apprentice.
Comment: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:01.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And I'm the apprentice's assistant.
Comment: 0,1:00:02.56,1:00:05.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Apprentice's assistant?
Comment: 0,1:00:07.04,1:00:08.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Comment: 0,1:00:08.56,1:00:09.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,To the new town.
Comment: 0,1:00:09.72,1:00:12.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's right across the bridge!
Comment: 0,1:00:13.56,1:00:15.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Luculia!
Comment: 0,1:00:20.24,1:00:22.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Alright see you later,Violet!
Comment: 0,1:00:23.28,1:00:24.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And, ehm...
Comment: 0,1:00:24.24,1:00:25.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's Taylor!
Comment: 0,1:00:26.28,1:00:29.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor.Keep working hard!
Comment: 0,1:00:34.64,1:00:36.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Comment: 0,1:00:36.60,1:00:38.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,A Doll like me.
Comment: 0,1:00:38.20,1:00:39.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And the man?
Comment: 0,1:00:41.80,1:00:45.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never seen him before.
Comment: 0,1:00:47.72,1:00:49.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is this the new town?
Comment: 0,1:00:49.28,1:00:52.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes, try reading this.
Comment: 0,1:00:53.64,1:00:57.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Lei... Leid... en city.
Comment: 0,1:00:58.12,1:01:00.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ehm... What is this one?
Comment: 0,1:01:01.12,1:01:02.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Rethorica district.
Comment: 0,1:01:02.80,1:01:04.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Rethorica district.
Comment: 0,1:01:05.32,1:01:06.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The eighth...
Comment: 0,1:01:09.28,1:01:10.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And twelve!
Comment: 0,1:01:12.64,1:01:14.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Comment: 0,1:01:26.32,1:01:27.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Taylor-sama.
Comment: 0,1:01:28.36,1:01:29.50,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Comment: 0,1:01:30.16,1:01:31.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And this is?
Comment: 0,1:01:31.56,1:01:34.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's called an elevator.
Comment: 0,1:01:36.40,1:01:41.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,They were introduced when they were buildingthe complex houses in the new town.
Comment: 0,1:01:41.44,1:01:42.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's a new technology.
Comment: 0,1:01:49.48,1:01:50.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,How do you use it?
Comment: 0,1:01:52.84,1:01:56.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I think...You have to pull this lever.
Comment: 0,1:02:01.24,1:02:02.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's not moving?
Comment: 0,1:02:09.80,1:02:11.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's moving!
Comment: 0,1:02:13.32,1:02:15.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That's the place!
Comment: 0,1:02:15.52,1:02:17.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'll lower it a bit.
Comment: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:23.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We are finally out!
Comment: 0,1:02:24.52,1:02:26.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It would have been faster using the stairs.
Comment: 0,1:02:28.40,1:02:29.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Comment: 0,1:02:31.28,1:02:32.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Oh my!?
Comment: 0,1:02:34.40,1:02:35.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery!
Comment: 0,1:02:36.20,1:02:38.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My! Thank you!
Comment: 0,1:02:38.32,1:02:41.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's from my mom!
Comment: 0,1:02:41.20,1:02:44.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Marty!There is a present from granny!
Comment: 0,1:02:45.68,1:02:48.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Comment: 0,1:02:48.92,1:02:50.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Comment: 0,1:02:50.88,1:02:52.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Comment: 0,1:02:52.76,1:02:54.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Snacks!
Comment: 0,1:03:13.44,1:03:17.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Did I... Look so desperate for one?
Comment: 0,1:03:19.64,1:03:20.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You did.
Comment: 0,1:03:32.88,1:03:37.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So Luculia is in Leiden right now?
Comment: 0,1:03:37.76,1:03:40.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.She was with a gentleman.
Comment: 0,1:03:42.16,1:03:46.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Oh! That must beLucilia-san's fiancé!
Comment: 0,1:03:47.00,1:03:49.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So she will retireonce she gets married, huh?
Comment: 0,1:03:50.52,1:03:53.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. She won't have to retire.
Comment: 0,1:03:53.16,1:03:56.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Seems that even if you get marriedyou can keep working.
Comment: 0,1:03:56.60,1:03:58.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,1:04:01.60,1:04:02.82,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It sure is a new era!
Comment: 0,1:04:03.32,1:04:04.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,A new era?
Comment: 0,1:04:05.04,1:04:07.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,If you have to retire because you want to marry a nice man
Comment: 0,1:04:07.76,1:04:09.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,then being a Doll is nothing but a self-display.
Comment: 0,1:04:11.68,1:04:14.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Being a Doll is just being at display?
Comment: 0,1:04:14.44,1:04:16.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So it was, until now.
Comment: 0,1:04:16.84,1:04:19.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So for both of you this is a form of display too?
Comment: 0,1:04:21.48,1:04:24.15,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Well... I wouldn't call me being display but...
Comment: 0,1:04:24.28,1:04:27.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My dream was to become the best Doll in the world.
Comment: 0,1:04:27.52,1:04:32.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Ah... And I... Could say that my dream was to become a novelist.
Comment: 0,1:04:33.36,1:04:35.66,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Novels... Is that true?
Comment: 0,1:04:35.80,1:04:40.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Actually I have written a short story, and submitted it somehow...
Comment: 0,1:04:40.20,1:04:42.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a way to be in display, I see.
Comment: 0,1:04:43.56,1:04:46.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Then? What's yours?
Comment: 0,1:04:48.32,1:04:50.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My... Way to show...
Comment: 0,1:04:53.20,1:04:54.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Master!
Comment: 0,1:04:54.64,1:04:58.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Don't call me master!It's time for the afternoon deliveries.
Comment: 0,1:05:56.56,1:05:58.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor-sama!
Comment: 0,1:06:08.28,1:06:09.42,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?
Comment: 0,1:06:09.92,1:06:10.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,1:06:11.52,1:06:15.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It's the first timesomeone buys clothes for me!
Comment: 0,1:06:16.64,1:06:18.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Comment: 0,1:06:19.12,1:06:22.66,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Clothes were hand-me-downs at the orphanage.
Comment: 0,1:06:23.48,1:06:25.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Having my own things somehow makes me happy.
Comment: 0,1:06:26.12,1:06:27.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I have to treasure them!
Comment: 0,1:06:30.60,1:06:31.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And this too!
Comment: 0,1:06:32.04,1:06:35.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This bear isvery very important for me!
Comment: 0,1:06:37.36,1:06:39.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Having things to treasure...
Comment: 0,1:06:40.08,1:06:45.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,really is a blessing, isn't it?
Comment: 0,1:06:48.96,1:06:53.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Nenne used to dothis for me too...
Comment: 0,1:07:03.44,1:07:06.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've already forgotten most things.
Comment: 0,1:07:06.88,1:07:10.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"These are magic words tokeep you safe."
Comment: 0,1:07:11.08,1:07:14.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Amy.You only have to recite that."
Comment: 0,1:07:15.40,1:07:20.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to becomea deliveryman, Taylor-sama?
Comment: 0,1:07:21.04,1:07:24.82,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Because master brought me my sister's letter.
Comment: 0,1:07:25.88,1:07:31.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I've already forgotten most of  my time with Nenne.
Comment: 0,1:07:31.56,1:07:33.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But this letter is still with me!
Comment: 0,1:07:33.88,1:07:37.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What my sister said. How my sister felt for me...
Comment: 0,1:07:38.32,1:07:40.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What master brought to me...
Comment: 0,1:07:43.24,1:07:45.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Was happiness.
Comment: 0,1:07:47.44,1:07:50.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery is a wonderful job.
Comment: 0,1:07:51.44,1:07:52.42,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,1:07:55.88,1:07:57.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Comment: 0,1:07:59.12,1:08:03.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I want to become a happiness carrier too.
Comment: 0,1:08:09.16,1:08:12.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,, Would you like to send your sister a letter?
Comment: 0,1:08:12.60,1:08:16.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But... I still can't read.
Comment: 0,1:08:17.32,1:08:21.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And also I don't know what I should write to Nenne.
Comment: 0,1:08:24.12,1:08:28.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor-sama, I'm a Doll.
Comment: 0,1:08:29.32,1:08:33.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let me help you?
Comment: 0,1:09:00.16,1:09:02.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Will Nenne like it?
Comment: 0,1:09:04.32,1:09:06.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will convey your feelings.
Comment: 0,1:09:18.44,1:09:20.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I... A...m.
Comment: 0,1:09:38.08,1:09:41.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What it is?Why did you call me in so early?
Comment: 0,1:09:45.96,1:09:47.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are we sending her back to the orphanage?
Comment: 0,1:09:48.24,1:09:51.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No. We have a request to deliver a letter.
Comment: 0,1:10:05.92,1:10:07.47,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Did you write it?
Comment: 0,1:10:08.00,1:10:09.14,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,1:10:10.84,1:10:12.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She taught me the characters.
Comment: 0,1:10:16.00,1:10:18.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The recipient is Amy Bartlett.
Comment: 0,1:10:19.96,1:10:21.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,There is no address.
Comment: 0,1:10:21.48,1:10:22.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Because we don't know it.
Comment: 0,1:10:23.44,1:10:27.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy Bartlett.Now she goes by Isabella York.
Comment: 0,1:10:28.20,1:10:31.67,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She's the successor of the York family.We know she went to a women's college, but...
Comment: 0,1:10:31.80,1:10:34.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We don't know what came of her after graduation.
Comment: 0,1:10:36.36,1:10:38.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she supposed to be your friend?
Comment: 0,1:10:39.88,1:10:42.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We kept exchanging letters for a while...
Comment: 0,1:10:43.08,1:10:43.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,1:10:44.96,1:10:46.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She has stopped replying.
Comment: 0,1:10:47.96,1:10:51.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,We assume that she managed to marry someone with a high standing.
Comment: 0,1:10:52.32,1:10:55.94,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But so far, her partner remains secret.
Comment: 0,1:10:56.20,1:10:59.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So you are telling me to go look for her!?
Comment: 0,1:10:59.72,1:11:00.86,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Please.
Comment: 0,1:11:01.44,1:11:05.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Please... Master!
Comment: 0,1:11:12.04,1:11:15.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I want to reach Nenne!
Comment: 0,1:11:37.52,1:11:41.22,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Only because there is no such thing asa letter unworthy of being delivered.
Comment: 0,1:11:43.04,1:11:46.74,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But I have a condition!
Comment: 0,1:12:53.48,1:12:55.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be here.
Comment: 0,1:12:58.72,1:13:03.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Dedication is fine but you should get some proper sleep.
Comment: 0,1:13:03.20,1:13:05.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,1:13:10.00,1:13:11.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It burns!
Comment: 0,1:13:11.92,1:13:15.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Oh right! We received a letter for you.
Comment: 0,1:13:28.32,1:13:29.46,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I found her.
Comment: 0,1:13:34.00,1:13:36.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,, So that was your condition, wasn't it?
Comment: 0,1:13:37.12,1:13:41.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yup! The other bike was already in tatters too...
Comment: 0,1:13:41.76,1:13:44.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Take care, okay?Taylor-chan.
Comment: 0,1:13:45.12,1:13:46.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,1:13:47.92,1:13:49.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You coming?
Comment: 0,1:13:51.36,1:13:52.34,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,1:13:54.40,1:13:55.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Comment: 0,1:13:55.92,1:13:56.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,1:14:05.36,1:14:08.98,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Violet.
Comment: 0,1:14:12.04,1:14:13.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Comment: 0,1:14:19.80,1:14:22.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!Taylor-sama!
Comment: 0,1:14:28.32,1:14:30.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,May your feelings...
Comment: 0,1:14:32.24,1:14:33.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,find a way to  reach her.
Comment: 0,1:14:44.12,1:14:47.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nobody really knew much
Comment: 0,1:14:47.36,1:14:49.74,Engsub,,0,0,0,,about Isabella being a heir to the York family.
Comment: 0,1:14:50.92,1:14:54.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,However, as long as you haveroyal blood in the Drossel kingdom
Comment: 0,1:14:54.32,1:14:56.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,no matter how much try to hide it,
Comment: 0,1:14:56.36,1:14:59.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,your marriage prospects can only be honorable nobles.
Comment: 0,1:15:05.12,1:15:08.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was comb through all the noble names.
Comment: 0,1:15:46.16,1:15:47.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Comment: 0,1:15:48.80,1:15:52.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,This is the mansion of this land's ruler. Count Nevilla.
Comment: 0,1:15:52.76,1:15:56.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,The village nearby seems to havefrequent audiences with the count.
Comment: 0,1:15:57.04,1:15:59.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But they've never seen the wifeliving in this mansion.
Comment: 0,1:15:59.68,1:16:01.39,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Or so everyone says.
Comment: 0,1:16:03.24,1:16:05.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,But they've heard from the guardsat the entrance.
Comment: 0,1:16:06.56,1:16:09.59,Engsub,,0,0,0,,It seems that the wife likes to wander near that back door
Comment: 0,1:16:09.72,1:16:11.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,at this time of the day.
Comment: 0,1:17:09.72,1:17:11.31,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Comment: 0,1:17:18.60,1:17:21.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I got a letter for you.
Comment: 0,1:17:22.16,1:17:24.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,For... me?
Comment: 0,1:17:26.92,1:17:29.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it. Isabe-
Comment: 0,1:17:30.68,1:17:32.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy Bartlett.
Comment: 0,1:17:40.12,1:17:41.18,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Comment: 0,1:18:01.64,1:18:05.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor Bartlett.
Comment: 0,1:18:09.68,1:18:10.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,No way...
Comment: 0,1:18:27.00,1:18:30.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"I... A...m..."
Comment: 0,1:18:32.68,1:18:35.35,Engsub,,0,0,0,,A nun told me.
Comment: 0,1:18:36.96,1:18:38.02,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"That Nenne..."
Comment: 0,1:18:38.92,1:18:43.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Chose to go somewherefar away for my sake."
Comment: 0,1:18:44.96,1:18:49.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"And even if we were far apart, you gave me a letterwith your feelings."
Comment: 0,1:18:52.36,1:18:53.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"So..."
Comment: 0,1:18:55.08,1:18:56.06,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"I..."
Comment: 0,1:19:00.28,1:19:03.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"I... Taylor Bartlett..."
Comment: 0,1:19:05.36,1:19:08.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Amy Bartlett's..."
Comment: 0,1:19:17.80,1:19:19.55,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Little sister."
Comment: 0,1:19:31.72,1:19:33.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,My...
Comment: 0,1:19:34.56,1:19:36.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Little sister...!
Comment: 0,1:20:18.44,1:20:21.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Taylor.
Comment: 0,1:20:37.16,1:20:38.38,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,1:20:39.24,1:20:42.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Violet helped her with the letter.
Comment: 0,1:20:45.56,1:20:48.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's...
Comment: 0,1:20:50.68,1:20:51.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Comment: 0,1:20:53.00,1:20:57.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. So glad...
Comment: 0,1:20:59.64,1:21:00.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne...
Comment: 0,1:21:03.32,1:21:04.87,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Nenne.
Comment: 0,1:21:19.96,1:21:21.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You're both the same, huh?
Comment: 0,1:21:25.92,1:21:27.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So she can already write?
Comment: 0,1:21:28.64,1:21:30.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Comment: 0,1:21:30.16,1:21:32.62,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She was just so small, you know?
Comment: 0,1:21:35.88,1:21:39.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I will write too. Letters for Taylor.
Comment: 0,1:21:40.48,1:21:41.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,And for Violet too.
Comment: 0,1:21:44.28,1:21:46.07,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Will you see that they reach them?
Comment: 0,1:21:46.64,1:21:47.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,1:21:50.48,1:21:53.95,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Some day, there might be someone elseto do that instead of me.
Comment: 0,1:22:14.24,1:22:16.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Master, you were crying back there, weren't you?
Comment: 0,1:22:17.16,1:22:19.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,You were the one crying.
Comment: 0,1:22:19.36,1:22:21.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you were crying too, master.
Comment: 0,1:22:21.36,1:22:22.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Comment: 0,1:22:25.40,1:22:26.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Say...
Comment: 0,1:22:27.28,1:22:29.79,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't want to talk to her?
Comment: 0,1:22:32.72,1:22:33.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Comment: 0,1:22:36.44,1:22:39.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Once I've grown up into a proper deliveryman...
Comment: 0,1:22:41.44,1:22:46.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,When that time comesI will bring her the letters myself!
Comment: 0,1:22:47.48,1:22:50.04,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So you haven't given up yet.
Comment: 0,1:22:50.16,1:22:52.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Of course not!After all, deliverymen...
Comment: 0,1:22:52.36,1:22:53.91,Engsub,,0,0,0,,What we carry around is...
Comment: 0,1:22:55.84,1:22:57.19,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Happiness.
Comment: 0,1:22:58.40,1:22:59.51,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 0,1:23:03.64,1:23:04.75,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Comment: 0,1:23:17.12,1:23:18.43,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Comment: 0,1:23:27.28,1:23:31.99,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Later, Taylor Bartlett was adopted into the Evergarden family.
Comment: 0,1:23:34.32,1:23:36.78,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Once she's old enough to work...
Comment: 0,1:23:37.80,1:23:38.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Comment: 0,1:23:38.76,1:23:40.27,Engsub,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Comment: 0,1:23:41.24,1:23:44.11,Engsub,,0,0,0,,She will start working hereas a deliveryman once again.
Comment: 0,1:23:45.56,1:23:46.83,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Delivery.
Comment: 0,1:23:50.92,1:23:52.63,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sir...
Comment: 0,1:23:54.32,1:24:00.03,Engsub,,0,0,0,,When will they finishthat tall building?
Comment: 0,1:24:05.32,1:24:06.54,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Soon enough.
Comment: 0,1:24:08.04,1:24:09.23,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Soon enough.
Comment: 0,1:25:01.00,1:25:07.71,Engsub,,0,0,0,,Taylor!
Comment: 0,1:25:36.00,1:25:44.00,Engsub,,0,0,0,,"Calling your nameis all I need to make our bonds everlasting."
